#: ../../source/index.rst:9
#: e99b1e52d6094e3cb0519ff05bc40621
msgid "Godot-FmodPlayer 是一个 Godot 4 GDExtension 插件，基于 FMOD Core API 提供音频播放、 混音、DSP 效果、3D 音频和性能监控功能。"
msgstr ""
"Godot-FmodPlayer is a Godot 4 GDExtension plugin based on the FMOD Core API. It provides audio playback, mixing, DSP effects, 3D audio, and performance monitoring."

#: ../../source/index.rst:12
#: bb2601f9c14e4985a7e2f20ddbcb8d6f
msgid "适合用于需要比 Godot 原生音频系统更细致控制的项目，例如动态混音、实时音效处理、 长音频流式播放、空间音频和 FMOD 底层 API 集成。"
msgstr ""
"It is suitable for projects that need finer control than Godot's built-in audio system, such as dynamic mixing, real-time audio processing, long streaming audio, spatial audio, and lower-level FMOD API integration."

#: ../../source/index.rst:16
#: 1a409c6a043349c9962016a4a2b968ed
msgid "主要功能"
msgstr "Key Features"

#: ../../source/index.rst:18
#: 984823167bd14da890f73569063878ab
msgid "支持 MP3、WAV、OGG、FLAC、MOD、XM、S3M、IT、MIDI 等音频格式"
msgstr "Supports audio formats such as MP3, WAV, OGG, FLAC, MOD, XM, S3M, IT, and MIDI."

#: ../../source/index.rst:19
#: 601f7c0cd25d4e27a7ba135bfba29210
msgid "支持流式加载、样本加载、内存加载和 Godot PCK 资源加载"
msgstr "Supports streaming, sample loading, memory loading, and loading resources from Godot PCK files."

#: ../../source/index.rst:20
#: 62abfbf24b5443d58e10ff32db39585a
msgid "提供 ``FmodAudioStreamPlayer``、``FmodAudioStreamPlayer2D`` 和 ``FmodAudioStreamPlayer3D`` 播放节点"
msgstr "Provides ``FmodAudioStreamPlayer``, ``FmodAudioStreamPlayer2D``, and ``FmodAudioStreamPlayer3D`` playback nodes."

#: ../../source/index.rst:21
#: a2ac4118517a4b3994288454ab31ad42
msgid "支持通道、通道组、音频总线和实时混音控制"
msgstr "Supports channels, channel groups, audio buses, and real-time mixing control."

#: ../../source/index.rst:22
#: 208e1507e5b94dd29f8744942a674a3c
msgid "提供混响、EQ、滤波、延迟、失真、压缩、频谱分析等 DSP 效果"
msgstr "Provides DSP effects such as reverb, EQ, filtering, delay, distortion, compression, and spectrum analysis."

#: ../../source/index.rst:23
#: 549b4ac0306c4556adbbb686c6af54d7
msgid "支持 FMOD CPU 与文件读取性能监控"
msgstr "Supports FMOD CPU and file I/O performance monitoring."

#: ../../source/index.rst:24
#: d1b94c5f82f34c4ea8f8205d7160df9d
msgid "提供编辑器导入器、音频预览和自定义资源类型"
msgstr "Provides an editor importer, audio preview, and custom resource types."

